---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="S-Reborn Lab"
	description="Doctor AI Academy와 S-Reborn Lab 허브입니다. S-Reborn Clinic Blog는 준비중입니다."
>
	<div class="lab-page">
		<header class="lab-page-head">
			<h1>S-Reborn Lab</h1>
			<p class="lab-page-lead">
				임상·AI·기록을 모은 실험실입니다. Doctor AI Academy는 아래에서 열 수 있고, S-Reborn Clinic Blog는 준비중입니다.
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="lab-hub-grid">
			<a class="lab-hub-card" href="/doctor-ai/">
				<span class="lab-hub-icon" aria-hidden="true">🩺</span>
				<h2 class="lab-hub-title">Doctor AI Academy</h2>
				<p class="lab-hub-desc">
					Fundamentals, Prompts, Cases, Tools — 임상의를 위한 AI 교육 시리즈.
				</p>
				<span class="lab-hub-cta">Academy로 이동 →</span>
			</a>
			<div class="lab-hub-card lab-hub-card--soon" aria-disabled="true">
				<span class="lab-hub-icon" aria-hidden="true">📰</span>
				<h2 class="lab-hub-title">S-Reborn Clinic Blog</h2>
				<p class="lab-hub-desc lab-hub-desc--soon">준비중</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
